      "content": "rebuilding sounds like a joke. i'm not talking about a \"small setback\" or some temporary slump. the math literally doesn't work. the debt is permanent. the damage to my family's name is permanent. there is no \"one small step\" that fixes a hole this deep. it feels like the only way to actually stop the noise and the feeling of being a total disgrace is to just... stop. to just make it all go away so it doesn't keep hurting everyone.",
